	\'95	\uc0\u8232 \'bd teaspoon garlic salt, or to taste\u8232 \
	\'95	\uc0\u8232 1 pinch ground white pepper, or to taste\u8232 \
	\'95	\uc0\u8232 1 lime, zested and juiced\u8232 \
